---
This little book builds a temperature converter — a library and the command line over it — in {{lang: TypeScript}}.
---

# About this book

A book is a corpus of looms read in one order. This one is a single chapter, :: [Converting temperatures], which writes a small converter and the shell that runs it. Loom finds the chapter beside this spine in the same corpus directory, so the book reaches it by name alone, with nothing imported by hand.

# The program [dist]

The converter writes its files into one directory, `dist`. This part places the chapter there: the anchor below names the chapter by its opening heading, and the book lays every file the chapter writes beneath this root.

::[Converting temperatures]
